{"tid":1178633,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴 上至球會下至球員 球迷 名宿 全部都係賤種狗","createTime":"2019-05-30T14:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T07:46:56.000Z","uid":5190,"like":66,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9f7c03b658ead830213e2867f351be745be2c341","tid":1178633,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死阿狗 唔係好撚串㗎咩<br />\n周圍撩事鬥非 阿狗po頭又鳩吹咩捧盃 最後乜柒都無我捧<br />\n<br />\n球會長期受波台狗關照 又自稱正統<br />\n球員 個個圍球證插水做戲 個個樣生到成隻狗樣咁<br />\n球迷 三日唔埋兩日就開抽水Post 其他大球會都冇做乜就比你係咁抽 雲加一定係史上最強 係教練之神 其他都只係好勁嘅足球教練<br />\n得到少少勢就不饒人 目空一切嗰種氣焰 我真係屌你老母啦<br />\n<br />\n既然講到咁撚神 做乜仲唔返嚟救下間狗廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下季得返自己一間「big6」踢歐霸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：巴迷（巴希亞）"},{"pid":"b9cf1f2dc60295e41eb3914b8d49a9907ef9d9af","tid":1178633,"uid":60658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"又搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d3fedad3e83dadf264bd03acfb8208373c60ec","tid":1178633,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9cf1f2dc60295e41eb3914b8d49a9907ef9d9af","tid":1178633,"uid":60658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"又搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"邊夠你嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abeef75f31e2ae5b046e1ca4bc3d3ee03b301da6","tid":1178633,"uid":5190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好波"},{"pid":"f27df90a996829053eafcf75e2f624f4aba621ca","tid":1178633,"uid":27416,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedB